根据“庇护号”（{{lang|en|Shelter}}）和“{{lang|en|A}}·{{lang|en|Z}}·格陵兰号”（{{lang|en|A.Z.Greenland}}）船只的报告，[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]][[科尔武岛|科尔武岛]]西北偏西方向约940公里洋面于8月5日出现一级飓风<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。“治安法官号”（{{lang|en|Magistrate}}）船只也在海上遇到这场风暴，之后船员弃船逃生<ref name="partagas-1" />。
